title: How to Balance it All: Friends, Family, Alone Time
itunes:title: How to Balance it All: Friends, Family, Alone Time
description:
Today we are discussing how we incorporate a balance in our lives with regards to spending time with friends, family and being alone.  We love to discuss productivity and getting things done, however at the end of the day it is so important to foster relationships in life to keep happy.  Enjoy this episode!
